</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="25" pageNumber="623" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph blockId="25.[1364,2570,2031,2648]" pageId="25" pageNumber="623">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1366,1624,2337,2371]" pageId="25" pageNumber="623">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
The Lake Chad Tateril is probably omnivorous,like other members of genus.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
